    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tropical-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_happy-01.m4a"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ごちそうさまでした\n遙子さんのチキン南蛮、本当に美味しかったです",
      "startTime": 2.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、良かった。寮のみんなに好評だったから\n{user}君にも食べてほしかったのよ",
      "startTime": 11.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "満腹です……遙子さんの料理を食べられるみんなは\n幸せ者ですね",
      "startTime": 17.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "美味しそうに食べてもらえると、私も幸せなの",
      "startTime": 19.4658329964,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "私、みんなが忙しいから料理当番を\n買って出てるって言ったでしょ？",
      "startTime": 27.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "でも……実は他にも理由があって",
      "startTime": 29.9545853775,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "最近みんながね、夕飯前に一緒に\n宿題をやってることが多いの",
      "startTime": 38.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "特に数学は聞かれてもぜんぜん分からないから\n料理をしてれば答えなくて済むかなー、って",
      "startTime": 44.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "なるほど、遙子さんは意外と策士なんですね",
      "startTime": 48.7496653875,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "でもね、みんなが勉強する姿を見ながら料理をしてると\n本当の家族みたいでとってもあったかい気持ちになるの",
      "startTime": 58.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "素敵ですね\nやっぱりサニピのみんなとよく食べるんですか？",
      "startTime": 63.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "そうね、サニピメンバーはもちろんだけど\n月ストのみんなと食べることもあるわ",
      "startTime": 70.6333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんはお料理の匂いを嗅いでほわほわ～って\nしちゃって、勉強に手がつかなくなりがちだし……",
      "startTime": 77.3986687641,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk010.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんと芽衣ちゃんは、いかにもつまみぐい\nしたそうにじーっと見つめてくることが多いわね",
      "startTime": 84.9804251035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "目に浮かびます。それにしても、遙子さんは\n本当にみんなの頼れるお姉さんなんですね",
      "startTime": 92.7999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk011.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってもらえると嬉しいわ\n……ふわぁ～",
      "startTime": 99.5999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk012.m4a",
      "text": "……あっごめんごめん。{user}君が\nいるのに、つい油断してあくびしちゃった",
      "startTime": 104.6999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "気にしないで下さい。でも、絶対に\n無理はしないで下さいね。俺が目を光らせてますから",
      "startTime": 110.6623046526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk013.m4a",
      "text": "きゃー、怖ーい\nでも……うん、キツくなったら頼らせてもらうね",
      "startTime": 118.3999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "いえ、キツくなくても\n元気一杯の時でも頼って下さい",
      "startTime": 124.9999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "遙子さんの忙しさは把握してます\nどこで急に疲れが出るか分かりませんからね",
      "startTime": 130.2999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk014.m4a",
      "text": "う、うん、分かったわ",
      "startTime": 133.300332721,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk015.m4a",
      "text": "……もう、そんな真剣な顔で言われたら\nびっくりしちゃうじゃない",
      "startTime": 140.8666646321,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_train-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4447.273548499993,
          "startTime": 145.3139381806
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――CM撮影当日",
      "startTime": 143.7139381806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk016.m4a",
      "text": "ふわぁぁ～～……\n……あ、あくびしちゃった。ごめんね",
      "startTime": 149.2999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫ですよ\nそれより……やっぱり疲れてますか？　心配です",
      "startTime": 154.5999979655,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk017.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、だいじょ～ぶ……だい、じょう、ぶ……",
      "startTime": 159.530449144,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk018.m4a",
      "text": "う～ん……",
      "startTime": 167.7953532297,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "は、遙子さん？　……俺にもたれて寝てしまった\n起こすのも悪いし、しばらくこのままにしておくか",
      "startTime": 176.7333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_train-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "train-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk019.m4a",
      "text": "ん……んん……っ\n……あ、ごめん、寝ちゃってたね",
      "startTime": 187.3333312988,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk020.m4a",
      "text": "でも、ちょっと寝たおかげですっきりしたよ\nよーし、お仕事頑張るぞー！",
      "startTime": 194.3333312988,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7971.737549500005,
          "startTime": 199.2860166646
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 8519.054218200012,
          "startTime": 199.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-hrk021.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ、もう設営が進んでるわね！　早速挨拶を……\nって、あら？　なんだかざわざわしてるみたい",
      "startTime": 207.4000142415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02/sud_vo_adv_card_hrk_07_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "……どうやら撮影機材にトラブルが発生したみたいで\n集合を一時間遅らせてほしいとのことです",
      "startTime": 215.3000142415,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawabeach-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawabeach-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
